{"tid":688992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想知點先可以令佢鐘意你既入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-06-03T17:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T17:38:54.000Z","uid":33185,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a317c72070cfffd2c7b3a44566addacf6cd624d","tid":688992,"uid":33185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔鐘意你既人無論你為佢付出幾多佢都唔會望你半眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何必做到自己咁無尊嚴？<br />\n人地搵你zip時間先嗲兩句咋傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你問心嗰句 如果佢係鐘意你會唔會因爲你對佢好唔好就有影響啊？<br />\n你對佢差 隔幾日先覆佢 佢係鐘意你既最後咪又會做狗咁比你控制住情緒 不能自拔<br />\n相反 佢唔鐘意你既 你做幾多都只係徒勞 仲可能chur親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一念放下 萬般自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前都有巴打講過一句好啱：「有啲感情唔代表可以成為一段感情」<br />\nMove on 啦<br />\n我都學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66447ac68d9d2da4cfab88dcd8a46312efbe1008","tid":688992,"uid":33185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"我知你有上連登 我係好掛住你 但我唔會再搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278e33ada47782507420d8108d187f497899fc39","tid":688992,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"我都學緊佛 想放下自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f186b2d7cdfb1f3609570555ac692876d7790c4d","tid":688992,"uid":33185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278e33ada47782507420d8108d187f497899fc39","tid":